3. Touch the Sources button at the top to choose what you want to display.

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

4. Touch the source of the content you wish to show and drag it to the desired display, or drag to All Displays on the left to show everywhere.

5. If you are using the Document Camera, touch the blue Doc Cam Control button at the bottom to bring up the Zoom Controls. 

6. When finished with the system, first press the Exit button in the lower right corner and then press Yes Shutdown System. This will power off all projectors and displays.
